comment_data.body: This kind of code should be guarded by `#if CYTHON_USE_TYPE_SLOTS` and also needs a replacement for the Limited-API case.
I'd move this to the top of the function and just `return` from it, so that we save the indentation in the rest of the implementation. The `#define'  doesn't even need a preprocessor guard.
